  "texts": [
    "This is the privileged information used during training.",
    "Control Sequence Generation: Each control sequence consists of 50 steps over a T = 5 s horizon with sampling time of 0.1 s. Control sequences u = (v, ω) are generated via a uniform distribution in [-1.0, 1.0] with v clipped to [0, 1] m/s.",
    "The robot state evolves via:x k+1 = x k + v k cos(ψ k)∆t, y k+1 =y k + v k sin(ψ k)∆t ψ k+1 = ψ k + ω k ∆t(10)Ground-Truth Distance Computation For each trajectory resulting from the j-th control sequence u j = (v j, ω j), ∀j = 1,..., N p, the minimum distance to the LiDAR point cloud P LiDAR is:d gt,j = min k, p∈PLiDAR x k,jy k,j -p 2 (11)Training Set-up: The probabilistic collision model (Sec.",
    "III-E) is trained in Equinox [28] on an RTX 5090 desktop.",
